      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the dish from the oven and add your <strong>udon noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p><p>Cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for 5-7 min further or until the noodles are tender and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>one-pot chilli & miso pork udon noodles</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
